INSTRUCTIONS
~~~~~~~~~~~~
	 F1-F5	Hold cards 1-5
	    F6	Play A credit
	    F7  Insert Max bet(5 credits, if you have any credits that is...)
	    F9	Insert a coin
	    F10	Deal cards
	ALT-F10	Exit (display stats) press mousebutton to exit
	HELP	Display current stats: money won or lost.

Set the icon's tool type to "VALUE=5" for nickels, "VALUE=25" for
quarters, and "VALUE=100" for dollars. Other settings are NOT recomended.
When run from the CLI, or no tool type is set, VALUE defaults to 5(nickels).


